@manual_otp
Feature: 99acres end-to-end rental property flow # features/end_to_end.feature:2
  As a logged-in 99acres user
  I want to search, filter, shortlist, and view owner contact details
  So that the complete rental property journey is validated
  Scenario: Complete end-to-end property search and owner contact flow  # features/end_to_end.feature:7
    When I log in using the test data mobile number                     # features/steps/common_steps.py:73
    And I wait 20 seconds for manual OTP entry                          # features/steps/common_steps.py:94
    And I verify the OTP and continue                                   # features/steps/common_steps.py:102
    And I search rental properties using the test data location         # features/steps/property_steps.py:14
    Then the search results page should be displayed                    # features/steps/common_steps.py:109
    When I close blocking popups on the search results page             # features/steps/filter_steps.py:9
    And I apply the 2 BHK filter                                        # features/steps/filter_steps.py:14
    And I apply the Flat/Apartment filter                               # features/steps/filter_steps.py:19
    And I apply the Owner filter                                        # features/steps/filter_steps.py:24
    And I apply the Single Men filter                                   # features/steps/filter_steps.py:29
    And I sort results by price low to high                             # features/steps/filter_steps.py:34
    Then all required filters should be applied                         # features/steps/filter_steps.py:52
    And filtered results should be visible                              # features/steps/filter_steps.py:39
    When I open the first property from search results                  # features/steps/property_steps.py:21
    And I switch to the property details window                         # features/steps/property_steps.py:26
    Then the property title and rent amount should be visible           # features/steps/property_steps.py:72
    When I click the shortlist button                                   # features/steps/property_steps.py:32
    And I open the owner details section                                # features/steps/property_steps.py:39
    And I click the view phone number button                            # features/steps/property_steps.py:45
    Then the contact section should be displayed                        # features/steps/property_steps.py:86

